WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:24.353 --> 00:00:26.735
If you have a long-lost friend

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:30.161
they may have been burning up 
with salsa fever

00:00:30.491 --> 00:00:33.205
and you would probably find 
them here in Tallinn

00:00:33.444 --> 00:00:35.790
in Casa de Baile dance school

00:00:36.232 --> 00:00:39.330
These rooms fill up with 
hundreds of dance fans

00:00:39.654 --> 00:00:43.315
who are spicing up their lives 
with some hot salsa

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:47.514
Salsa is the most popular dance 
in the world – and a lifestyle

00:00:48.135 --> 00:00:51.827
its popularity in Estonia 
owes a lot to Casa de Baile

00:00:52.061 --> 00:00:55.649
Ten years ago it was difficult 
to find a place to learn it

00:00:55.871 --> 00:00:58.098
and the parties were held 
perhaps only once quarterly

00:00:58.386 --> 00:00:59.991
Now it is normal to attend parties

00:01:00.373 --> 00:01:02.828
on almost every day of the week

00:01:03.376 --> 00:01:07.418
biggest parties are held in Bastioni aed 
and Cubanita Live Cafe

00:01:08.227 --> 00:01:12.342
Casa de Baile is the pillar of 
Estonian salsa culture

00:01:12.875 --> 00:01:17.165
During the eight years of 
Casa de Baile’s existence

00:01:17.506 --> 00:01:22.915
we have taught the basic steps to 
probably 10,000 people

00:01:23.156 --> 00:01:25.768
People have made lots of friends

00:01:26.175 --> 00:01:28.270
some even a partner for life

00:01:29.061 --> 00:01:31.950
In salsa, it doesn’t matter 
if you’re rich or poor

00:01:32.028 --> 00:01:33.635
Estonian or Russian,

00:01:33.955 --> 00:01:35.172
business man or handyman

00:01:35.332 --> 00:01:37.092
If you enjoy dancing

00:01:37.158 --> 00:01:39.445
you are equal with others

00:01:39.736 --> 00:01:44.900
Salsaseriaal follows six active people 
dancing and developing themselves

00:01:45.494 --> 00:01:46.354
Here they are

00:01:51.515 --> 00:01:56.967
Salsaseriaal is an interesting 
experiment we embarked upon

00:01:57.906 --> 00:02:00.729
to promote salsa culture to wider public

00:02:01.362 --> 00:02:05.349
and show that learning to dance 
can be quite easy

00:02:06.286 --> 00:02:09.970
I have near zero dance experience

00:02:10.286 --> 00:02:13.097
Absolutely! I Don’t know dance at all

00:02:13.695 --> 00:02:17.474
and i find it exciting to start from zero

00:02:17.786 --> 00:02:18.535
and see what happens

00:02:19.233 --> 00:02:21.794
I haven’t dance much... at all

00:02:22.350 --> 00:02:24.318
I’ve never actively pursued dancing

00:02:25.564 --> 00:02:31.068
but I am hoping to follow 
the steps and learn quickly

00:02:31.567 --> 00:02:34.938
I am a little nervous before the 
first class but hopes are high

00:02:35.265 --> 00:02:37.389
I don’t have many expectations

00:02:38.022 --> 00:02:39.461
But I like to learn new things

00:02:40.751 --> 00:02:43.218
And this is certainly new for me

00:02:43.566 --> 00:02:46.419
I have thought about 
how the first class would be

00:02:46.510 --> 00:02:48.594
But you can’t really visualise it

00:02:48.704 --> 00:02:49.967
What’s gonna happen there

00:02:50.323 --> 00:02:50.966
Who I’m gonna meet

00:02:51.096 --> 00:02:52.275
The other people

00:02:52.462 --> 00:02:53.475
How’s the music gonna sound

00:02:53.548 --> 00:02:54.625
How I would be

00:02:54.677 --> 00:02:55.696
Would I stumble

00:02:55.769 --> 00:02:56.761
You know, all that

00:02:56.843 --> 00:03:00.283
I know that one should wear 
shoes not sneakers

00:03:01.511 --> 00:03:04.803
I am a little nervous 
before the first time, yes

00:03:05.075 --> 00:03:07.064
Because I really can’t imagine it yet

00:03:07.581 --> 00:03:10.506
My expectations – I am very excited 
by the way, holding my breath

00:03:11.005 --> 00:03:13.868
I am hoping people won’t notice 
how clumsy I am

00:03:14.133 --> 00:03:18.224
I hope my partner won’t be 
very light on her feet, either

00:03:18.516 --> 00:03:20.848
Somehow, I don’t expect it to be easy

00:03:21.285 --> 00:03:25.305
because doing too many turns

00:03:26.566 --> 00:03:28.489
will make my head spin

00:03:28.826 --> 00:03:31.362
And it’s gonna disturb my good mood

00:03:31.681 --> 00:03:33.189
which may make me dislike the classes

00:03:33.909 --> 00:03:35.929
And turn me moody

00:03:37.106 --> 00:03:38.117
I expect

00:03:39.064 --> 00:03:40.533
nice atmosphere

00:03:41.693 --> 00:03:43.886
And I don’t exactly know 
what’s gonna happen

00:03:44.189 --> 00:03:46.146
I am a little excited, I guess

00:03:46.545 --> 00:03:48.306
about the new challenge

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:51.469
I expect it to be a lot of fun

00:03:51.791 --> 00:03:57.647
I am hoping for these Mondays and 
Wednesdays to be very energetic

00:03:59.499 --> 00:04:01.593
Salsa is the most popular 
partnerdance in the world

00:04:01.673 --> 00:04:04.100
Salsa means sauce in Spanish

00:04:04.393 --> 00:04:08.881
spicy sauce used in many 
Latin-American dishes

00:04:09.381 --> 00:04:11.673
Salsa’s roots are in Cuban son-music

00:04:11.943 --> 00:04:14.740
Which developed into popular 
New York style called Mambo

00:04:15.028 --> 00:04:18.953
That’s why salsa is considered 
to be born in both Cuba and the US

00:04:21.157 --> 00:04:24.840
It’s a dance based on improvization, where 
the man leads and the woman follows

00:04:25.346 --> 00:04:29.429
This makes it possible to dance with someone 
even if you’ve never seen them before

00:04:29.700 --> 00:04:31.348
and anywhere in the world

00:04:31.746 --> 00:04:33.494
and it can always be a pleasant experience

00:04:40.401 --> 00:04:47.687
I am expecting all the best, 
that’s why I want to learn salsa

00:04:48.573 --> 00:04:53.399
I am hoping that salsa would 
give me new energy

00:04:54.249 --> 00:04:56.688
because I am also young at heart, 
not only based on my age

00:04:57.686 --> 00:05:01.246
We know now their expectations 
before the first class

00:05:01.997 --> 00:05:05.027
In the next episode we will 
get to know Cristo and Kristel

00:05:05.569 --> 00:05:09.247
and experience our sixpack’s 
first salsa class

00:05:09.627 --> 00:05:11.672
We will see whether it’s difficult

00:05:12.039 --> 00:05:13.306
or fun and addictive

00:05:13.799 --> 00:05:16.568
and find out who’s gonna 
haul the girls up by their arms

